Package org.neo4j.internal.id

Class BufferingIdGeneratorFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.internal.id.BufferingIdGeneratorFactory
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IdGeneratorFactory
    public class BufferingIdGeneratorFactory
extends Object
implements IdGeneratorFactory
    Wraps IdGenerator so that ids can be freed using reuse marker at safe points in time, after all transactions which were active at the time of freeing, have been closed.
